$ Gerald E. Aardsma

Aardsma vermutet, dass §1koe-6-1 nicht *im 480. Jahr* sondern *im 1480. Jahr* heissen müsste. (→ http://www.biblicalchronologist.org/answers/millennium.php[What is the missing millennium discovery?])

Er vermutet die Arche auf dem ~Cilo Dağı~ (→ http://www.biblicalchronologist.org/answers/ark.php[In Search of Noah's Ark]).

Er glaubt, dass ~Mt. Yeroham~ der → biblisches/Orte/Berg-Sinai ist
 (→ http://www.biblicalchronologist.org/answers/sinai_location.php[Where is Mt. Sinai located?], → http://www.biblicalchronologist.org/answers/sinai_arabia.php[Does the Bible say Mt. Sinai is in Saudi Arabia]).

